The purpose of this test plan is to define the testing approach, scope, objectives, risks, and deliverables for the VWO login and dashboard workflow. This plan validates successful authentication, dashboard access, and error handling for invalid login attempts.

## 3. Background
The application under test includes a login page for user authentication and a dashboard page accessible only after successful login. A valid login must navigate to the dashboard, while an invalid login must show an error page.

